carrental

Class Lease

  • java.lang.Object
    • carrental.Lease

  • public class Lease
extends java.lang.Object
    This is entity class represents Lease a car to customer. Each Lease has id, dates when the car was leased, when the car should be returned and when the car was really returned. Furthermore each lease has a customer who borrowed the car and the car which was rent.
